<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣٣ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَقَوْلُهُمْ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" الْمُسْتَحِي مَحْرُومٌ "</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٣٤ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَقَوْلُهُمْ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" عَجِّلُوا بِالصَّلاةِ قَبْلَ الْفَوْتِ، وَعَجِّلُوا بِالتَّوْبَةِ قَبْلَ الْمَوْتِ "</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
